        <h2>The Concept</h2>
        <p>When talking about investment, the word growth came into my mind.</p>
        <p>
            The word growth were than extracted and combine with their corporate identity to produce color scheme and simple
            graphics.
        </p>

        <div class="meta color">
            <img loading="lazy" src="/img/bkpm/bkpm-logo.svg" width="62" height="48" alt="BKPM Logo">
