                <li style="background: #263D93"></li>
                <li style="background: #E3D553"></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <ol class="zero">
            <li>
                Extracted the meaning of growth into the word
                <strong>seed</strong>
                which symbolized as the color of green.
            </li>
            <li>
                For the seed to grow, it need
                <strong>water</strong>
                and
                <strong>sun</strong>, both were symbolize as the color of blue and yellow.
            </li>
            <li>
                The
                <strong>growth</strong>
                itself was symbolize by a simple arrow pointing upward.
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>
